---
title: Hoisin Beef & Garlic Rice Bowl with Lime & Mint
description: This sizzling hoisin-infused beef bowl is a joy unparalleled. Simplicity is the winner here, with a garnish of mint and a squeeze of fresh lime being the crowning glory on this quick and easy weeknight winner.

*Unfortunately, this week's Asian greens were in short supply, so we've replaced them with broccolini.  Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asian-beef-makrut-lime-bowl-3e291639.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/asian-beef-lime-bowl-5e85340b808a563253714342-21bf723b.pdf
cuisine: Asian
